&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Consultant Physician in Acute Medicine - 10 sessions per week&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Our team of acute physicians describe themselves as a passionate team; because of their fantastic progress the last 5 years we are looking to further expand our acute medical workforce and portfolio of acute services.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are looking for a proactive, forward thinking and dynamic individual to join our expanding team. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The acute medicine team is located in a purpose built 59 bed acute medical unit, adjacent to the ambulatory care unit and emergency department, and in close proximity to the surgical assessment unit and critical care units.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are actively recruiting substantive posts to establish an acute physician consultant model of 12 consultants; and concurrently to an acute frailty/geriatrician consultant model of 5 consultants.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The role involves working alongside a multi-disciplinary team covering key service areas such as the Emergency Department, SDEC areas, and our inpatient acute assessment areas.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Our strategy for Acute Medicine involves:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ü &lt;em&gt;investing in people &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ü &lt;em&gt;investing in equipment &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ü &lt;em&gt;investing in the estate &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ü &lt;em&gt;investing in clinical pathways &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you are enthusiastic about Acute Medicine and delivering quality care, then you should join our team.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you desire a flexible job plan which offer a favourable work-life balance in the face of changes in clinical activities &amp; demands, then you should join our team.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;If you are seeking opportunities to lead on clinical service developments, then you should join our team.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Providing candidates have an interest in acute medicine, the team welcomes applications from colleagues with accreditation in for example, older people’s medicine, diabetic medicine, chest medicine etc who are seeking a hybrid post. The applicant should hold a CCT or demonstrate working toward achievement within 6 months&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Suzy Collins on 0161 419 4036&lt;/p&gt;
